<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="HappyFlower" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />来得正好！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我问你，<delay8 />你知道反应<delay8 />是什么吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像这样子活动身体<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎么样？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我看起来非常高兴对吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比光用言语表达更能传达内心的想法<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
