<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎么样？<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不管是什么事情，<delay8 />
