<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有兴趣的话，就用用看这招吧。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="Pardon" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay8 />我想到了一个有趣的反应，<delay20 />
正想向你展示一下呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就这么简单。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我会在想要稍微表现得<delay8 />
