<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我觉得记住它没什么损失啦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="IdeaBulb" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我今天心情特别好，<delay20 />
